A User receives a Notification if another User Likes his/her Post
A User receives a Notification if another User Likes his/her Comment

A User Blocked from a Community can not Like a Post in that Community
A User Blocked from a Community can not Like a Comment in that Community

A User that is Blocked by another User can not Like a Post on that User's Wall
A User that is Blocked by another User can not Like a Comment on that User's Wall

A User cannot Like a Post that is not Published
A User cannot Like a Comment that is not Published

If a Post is Deleted all its Likes are Deleted also
A Like does not show the User that Liked it

A User can Like a Post
A User can Like a Comment

A User receives a Notification if another User Likes his Comments
A User will receive a Notification if another User Likes his/her Comment

A User receives a Notification if another User Likes that User's Post
